{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the initial state of a pack. The state of a pack becomes known by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the time the shared "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object sends the first"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" about the pack. For inactive"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs, you must explicitly request a progress update using the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An invalid pack always has a state of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateInvalid","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":", never","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackstate\/mlnofflinepackstateunknown"]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@E@MLNOfflinePackState@MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","role":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"case"},"abstract":[{"text":"It is unknown whether the pack is inactive, active, or complete.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/removePack:withCompletionHandler:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed."}],"title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text"